{"tid":1262342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有前無線新聞部記者請你入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-06-27T15:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T16:36:17.000Z","uid":213740,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a0eb887e1d781a67e523048908fa75beb920b4","tid":1262342,"uid":213740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:50:16.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過呢場仗成敗嘅關鍵喺你哋身上？<br />\n<br />\n而家打緊民意戰<br />\n大家都好努力想話俾全香港，甚至全世界聽我哋嘅訴求<br />\n但無論幾努力都好<br />\n只要cctvb一個抹黑報導就輕易大量洗腦<br />\n我哋做嘅所有嘢都係白廢<br />\n我知道其實好多前線記者都係黃底<br />\n只係礙於高層阻撓先要被迫歪曲事實<br />\n而背後嘅幕後黑手就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">袁志偉呢條地下黨員</span></span><br />\n所以我哋首先要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打擊袁志偉，甚至無線新聞部嘅公信力</span></span><br />\n希望你哋會俾到一手資料我哋<br />\n等我哋將袁志偉嘅惡行宣揚岀去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a86538a3f5d627d950225fff398dde71c57277","tid":1262342,"uid":213740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:57:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d54fdda8c7906c8a6b169d53f282378146b652e4","tid":1262342,"uid":213740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:00:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"55d238a05551d3853c9213bd763f837e2fc93e57","tid":1262342,"uid":213740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:00:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"422d768503bf6f5ef732bcf01079572af7b39bf4","tid":1262342,"uid":85803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e274a3a7197996fcd43621be705b50bb56eedcc5","tid":1262342,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29a8c79090b5f43907b3b94c696d8ef50f45af5d","tid":1262342,"uid":213740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime